==English==

===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*kelh₁-}}
* First attested in 1541.
* Borrowed from {{bor|en|la|acclāmātiō|acclāmātiō, acclāmātiōnis|calling, exclamation, shout of approval}}, from {{m|la|acclamo||shout approval or disapproval of, shout out at}}, from {{m|la|ad||toward}} + {{m|la|clamo||cry out}}
* Compare French {{m|fr|acclamation}}.

